{"tid":1861653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎爆發逾月，港府終製香港疫情地圖","createTime":"2020-02-04T08:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T08:41:44.000Z","uid":132380,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5c7c2d23d1ec6b6b099b9d0eb2d72d957ab6879c","tid":1861653,"uid":132380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:27:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZaYsjiw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZaYsjiw.png&h=58f8c1bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情爆發超過一個月，港府終於製作了一個網站集合所有資料的官方地圖，用手機或電腦都能隨時查看。<br />\n<br />\n本港至今已有至少15宗武漢肺炎確診個案，政府終製作了新網頁，定時更新確診和懷疑個案、過去14天內確診個案曾經逗留過的建築物、過去14天內確診個案曾經乘搭的公共交通工具及日期、檢疫中心、急症室等候時間、以及個案趨勢圖等。<br />\n<br />\n地圖 <a href=\"https://chp-dashboard.geodata.gov.hk/nia/zh.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchp-dashboard.geodata.gov.hk%2Fnia%2Fzh.html&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlJhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=390cc3ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chp-dashboard.geodata.gov.hk/nia/zh.html</a>"},{"pid":"149adc9cd50c08179158b7c494b747ab4e61742b","tid":1861653,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:28:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0407dc05335c28190f1f96c547f27d40c544f58","tid":1861653,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:28:41.000Z","msg":"符合呈報準則個案？！"},{"pid":"99db34ef9ab70369541231b30f8774cb230310fa","tid":1861653,"uid":126219,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:30:26.000Z","msg":"死字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b634016fc1967ca1473ae4e04941b3947e3b6572","tid":1861653,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T08:30:58.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"